{"tid":2094402,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"四眼禮志呢期個fb食左藥？","createTime":"2020-07-04T15:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T17:29:57.000Z","uid":6070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a92a0f3207ce05c953e5127afffe1d165b9387b4","tid":2094402,"uid":6070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"好心提多次，有案在身者，唔好接受傳媒訪問，除非你想從政，先考慮自己官司。<br />\n<br />\n即使不幸被判入獄，須服刑兩年或以上者，仲有機會試兩項提早釋放計劃，包括釋前就業計劃、監管下釋放計劃，屆時要見「監管下釋囚委員會」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自私啲，細心諗諗每個對自己有利嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n唔係每個人都走到，唔係每個走到嘅人都有政治庇護，唔係每個有政治庇護嘅人都有人照顧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你真心嗌過口號，甚至當梁天琦係精神領袖，就請心存尊重，唔好玩膠。你哋做緊嘅事，謝偉俊幾個月前已經做緊。<br />\n<br />\n甚至早前個個政客都改做「康復香港　時代抗疫」，我都覺得有問題，不過隨大家中意啦。<br />\n開哂turbo咁屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f167c71fec42a6d94daee1a917a966d13d5e4c5f","tid":2094402,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T15:12:01.000Z","msg":"選舉近了"},{"pid":"e4ac3b4653833600a04277ac3665a65aa8cde075","tid":2094402,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T15:13:34.000Z","msg":"呢種議論咁有料嘅人我地竟然只係選佢入去打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21641cd66b129836fc85a9c090b227edf014f34c","tid":2094402,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:29:57.000Z","msg":"飲咗通渠水<br />\n諗通晒"}]}